                    <h3 data-uuid="2a112ff7e79c4c74967679d8ede8d43a" class="mod">A Divided Nation, 1845–1865</h3>
                    <p class="mod" data-uuid="da8bc53a08ee4e849b121ec1afccedf4">Sectional tensions increased throughout the 1850s until they reached a boiling point with the election of Abraham Lincoln as president. Shortly after the election South Carolina seceded from the Union.</p>
